China Urges ConocoPhillips to Clean Up Oil Spill, Bureau Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-08-17T14:25:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-17/china-urges-conocophillips-to-clean-up-oil-spill-bureau-says.html
China said  ConocoPhillips (COP)  must
finish the required cleanup of an  oil spill  in Penglai 19-3
filed in northern China by Aug. 31 or face "stiffer measures",
according to the State Oceanic Administration.  ConocoPhillips must seal an oil leak of the B Platform and
clean up the spill in the C platform, the agency said in a
statement on its website today, citing a meeting between the
environmental protection department and officials from the
American company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
William Bi in Beijing at 
